    <div id="faq-content">
        <div class="section" id="for-tutors">
            <h1>For tutors</h1>
            <div class="question" id="question1" onclick="openQuestion1()">
                <h3><span id="sign1"><svg aria-hidden="true" id="plus-svg" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas"
                            data-icon="plus" class="svg-inline--fa fa-plus fa-w-14" role="img"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
                            <path fill="currentColor"
                                d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z">
                            </path>
                        </svg></span>Am I limited to teaching one subject?</h3>
                <span class="answer" id="answer1">No, you are not.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="question" id="question2" onclick="openQuestion1()">
                <h3><span id="sign2"><svg aria-hidden="true" id="plus-svg" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas"
                            data-icon="plus" class="svg-inline--fa fa-plus fa-w-14" role="img"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
                            <path fill="currentColor"
                                d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z">
                            </path>
                        </svg></span>Will I be paid to tutor?</h3>
                <span class="answer" id="answer2">Currently, this is a free service. However, in the future, we would
                    like to implement a credit system so that our tutors can get paid for the hard work that they
                    do.</span>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="section" id="for-students">
            <h1>For students</h1>
            <div class="question" id="question3" onclick="openQuestion1()">
                <h3><span id="sign3"><svg aria-hidden="true" id="plus-svg" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas"
                            data-icon="plus" class="svg-inline--fa fa-plus fa-w-14" role="img"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
                            <path fill="currentColor"
                                d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z">
                            </path>
                        </svg></span>Who are the tutors?</h3>
                <span class="answer" id="answer3">Tutors come from a variety of backgrounds, including former and
                    current one-on-one tutors and others who may have expertise in the subject area. These tutors are
                    very passionate about helping students succeed.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="question" id="question4" onclick="openQuestion1()">
                <h3><span id="sign4"><svg aria-hidden="true" id="plus-svg" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas"
                            data-icon="plus" class="svg-inline--fa fa-plus fa-w-14" role="img"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
                            <path fill="currentColor"
                                d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z">
                            </path>
                        </svg></span>How do I know my tutor will help me?</h3>
                <span class="answer" id="answer4">You may view the tutor’s profile page to see their rating prior to
                    scheduling a meeting with them. Their students have given them the rating after each of their
                    sessions.
                </span>
            </div>

            <div class="question" id="question5" onclick="openQuestion1()">
                <h3><span id="sign5"><svg aria-hidden="true" id="plus-svg" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas"
                            data-icon="plus" class="svg-inline--fa fa-plus fa-w-14" role="img"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
                            <path fill="currentColor"
                                d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z">
                            </path>
                        </svg></span>Do I need to pay for this service?</h3>
                <span class="answer" id="answer5">Currently, it is a free service. However, in the future, we would like
                    to implement a credit system so that our tutors can get paid for the hard work that they do.
                </span>
            </div>

            <div class="question" id="question6" onclick="openQuestion1()">
                <h3><span id="sign6"><svg aria-hidden="true" id="plus-svg" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas"
                            data-icon="plus" class="svg-inline--fa fa-plus fa-w-14" role="img"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
                            <path fill="currentColor"
                                d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z">
                            </path>
                        </svg></span>Is the tutoring one-on-one or do I need to do it with a group?</h3>
                <span class="answer" id="answer6">For now, all of our sessions are only one-on-one.</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="general">
            <h1>General</h1>
