                                d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z">
                            </path>
                        </svg></span>How does the credit system work?</h3>
                <span class="answer" id="answer7">Credits can be purchased in the shop. Each session takes a specific
                    amount of credits, which is stated in the session page. These credits will be deposited in the
                    tutor’s account and removed from the student’s account. These credits will then be available for the
                    tutor to convert into currency.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
